text: main ( ) { int n1 , n2 , i , t , gcd , lcm ; scanf ( "%d" , & t ) ; while ( t -- ) { scanf ( "%d\t %d" , & n1 , & n2 ) ; for ( i = 1 ; i <= n1 && i <= n2 ; ++ i ) { if ( n1 % i == 0 && n2 % i == 0 ) gcd = i ; } lcm = ( n1 * n2 ) / gcd ; printf ( "\n" ) ; printf ( "%d\t%d" , gcd , lcm ) ; } }
